name: smtp-monitoring
description: Skill dla monitorowania połączeń SMTP i testowania wysyłania emaili
topics:
  - smtp
  - email
  - monitoring
  - testing
applyTo:
  - path: "**/mailer/**"
  - path: "**/tests/**"
  - path: "**/*.py"
languageDetection:
  preferredLanguage: python
  patterns:
    - "smtp"
    - "email"
    - "monitor"
